  <p>At intake, an LLM classifies and extracts key fields. At triage, a prediction scores urgency or value. At decision, real-time decisioning selects the next best action with constraints. At action, a GenAI connector drafts the email or note. Feedback logs outcomes to improve prompts and models.</p>
  <p>Use Process AI for predictions, Decisioning for arbitration, and GenAI connectors for bounded language tasks.</p>
